      • ResourceReporter

        public ResourceReporter(Reportable informationSource)
        Constructor for a new ResourceReporter. Note that although any Reportable is accepted you should make sure that only subtypes of Res are passed to this constructor. Otherwise the number of column titles and their individual headings will differ from the actual content collected by this reporter.
        Parameters:
        informationSource - desmoj.core.simulator.Reportable : The Res to report about.
